	ugh\\\, youll cry\\\, youll cringe as you join the video wizards of Collid
	e-O-Scope on a voyage of sight and sound\\\, exploring the wonderful\\\, w
	eird\\\, marvelously messy spectrum of Pride!Collide-O-Scope is the greate
	st show anywhere! Dina MartinaHalf video art installation and half stoner 
